oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Country store
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A country store in the upper Sequatchie Valley. A dirt road, enclosed by wooden fence, leads to the building. Two men are outside, one of which is standing on a porch held up by rocks.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
